# Recommended Next.js Project Structure

This structure organizes the project logically, separating concerns and making it easy to locate and manage files.

/src
├── app/ # Next.js App Router
│ ├── layout.tsx # Root layout
│ └── page.tsx # Main page component
│
├── components/ # Reusable components
│ ├── ui/ # Small, generic UI elements
│ │ ├── CustomCursor.tsx
│ │ └── NavButton.tsx
│ │
│ ├── layout/ # Major layout components
│ │ ├── Header.tsx
│ │ ├── Footer.tsx
│ │ └── NavOverlay.tsx
│ │
│ └── sections/ # Main page sections
│ ├── HeroSection.tsx
│ ├── ProjectsSection.tsx
│ └── ClosingSection.tsx
│
├── hooks/ # Custom React Hooks
│ └── useMousePosition.ts
│
├── lib/ # Library/helper functions
│ └── utils.ts
│
└── styles/ # Global styles
└── globals.css
